  "Description": {
    "English": "Adds <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Terrain Manipulation</span> capability to the laser array of the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Minotaur Heavy Exosuit Hybrid</span>.<br><br>A special mount allows the rapid deployment of a high-energy terrain excavator, without risking clogging the Minotaur's delicate joints and servos with dirt.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "增加<span class=\"name name-stellar\">弥诺陶洛斯混合重型套件</span>激光阵列的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">地形操纵</span>能力。<br><br>一个可让高能地形挖掘机快速部署的特殊装置，而不会出现泥土堵塞弥诺陶洛斯脆弱接合处和伺服系统的危险。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彌諾陶洛斯重型強化套裝混合體</span>的雷射陣列新增<span class=\"name name-stellar\">地形改造</span>功能。<br><br>這特殊配件能快速部署高能量地形挖掘機，不會害彌諾陶洛斯精密的關節和伺服卡灰塵。"
  },
